{"word":"πνίγω","slug":"πνίγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πνίγω</el></b> [origin unclear] ‘grab or enclose tightly in such a way that <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> can no longer live’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b>strangle <a href='B:470 18:28'>Mt 18:28</a>;</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on loss of breath in water, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>drown <a href='B:480 5:13'>Mk 5:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of plants as victims of encroaching weeds <b>choke <a href='B:470 13:7'>Mt 13:7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πνέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πνικτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}